Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This video is a special release provided to all of you by Shogakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When watching this video, please brighten the room and watch at a distance from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last week, you all explored Beika City and found many different stores, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of stores were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A grocery store!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flower shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A supermarket!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s family owns a liquor store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called Kojima Liquor Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you need to pick one store as your example.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find out what the store is selling, the plans of the owners, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it doesn't have to be a store, for example, a post office or a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask what kind of work they do, what is difficult about their work...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find out as much as you can and then make a presentation about it in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, you can start discussing which store you're going to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, which one will we choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, let's go to a store that sells rice with eel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we do, they can treat us with delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, this one is on Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Where's mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is so Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, where do you think we should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! What do you think, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I would be interested to go to that beauty salon in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beauty saloon? In front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is unique and will be very helpful for the development of Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Unique and helpful for the development of Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.13,Title,,0,0,0,,THE TARGET IS KOGORO!!\NTHE DETECTIVE BOYS' SECRET REPORT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this is related to the school, I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, don't hesitate to ask any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's get straight to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of work you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In general, being a professional means receiving different task from clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From investigations to direct assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for me, wherever I go, cases just seem to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have to unravel the tricks of the criminals instead of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Except the one who does that is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you do best or what do you like the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Best at... Like the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, investigations with young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And tons of free drinks while investigating at club is lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what I mean is, there is no place for preference in detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of young girls, my dad recently dated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then my mother severely scolded him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of some smell of perfume from his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell your dad to go to a restaurant with tempura after the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After sitting at the counter for an hour, he will carry smell of oil instead of perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're always go there so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I really love tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uncle, you brought that on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, since you are married, why don't you live with your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your wife just kicked you out because he played around with young girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I figured too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be irreconcilable differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or it could be because of financial problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what is your annual income?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are these kids really elementary school students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, just answer their questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't joke with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I keep hanging around with these little monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is it so late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well you guys, I'm sorry, but I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that? Did he just ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're going to go shadowing Detective Mouri to observe his actual working environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we'll go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure he doesn't go to any tempura restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, here comes the great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the ninja from the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He will notice them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And send them away or shake them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Notice them already. Are you a detective or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:52.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}On the first track from the Touto loop line, a train will arrives at Sibahama station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He will notice you if you get off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he just left before the doors closed. That means he's already noticed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He jumped off because he thought there was 500 yen on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like it's just a game token or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd get off because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do now, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't follow him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, in 8-9 out of 10 he will take the next train, so we just have to wait for him at the next station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, he will most likely now on the train a bit further back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really is one train further back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trash can was a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was embarrassed, so he wouldn't get on the same train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same happens when you miss the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like a real detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I am a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masaya Murakami (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2-3-2-4-2-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's staking out that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, his name is Murakami Masaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10 days ago, a wealthy family asked him to find out about the life of their only daughter's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like that! Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His acting skill is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it so that no one knows he's a detective, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recently read about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The basic rule for a professional stakeout is to blend in with the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely his stupid behavior is planned to be part of this Saturday park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's truly a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was his true face,\Nthe face of a mad horse-racing fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he's not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's being cautious for some reason, and that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Right in front of my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we've called the police right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we remember the car's license plate number!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't the criminals have been caught already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was he kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminals must have a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this was done by people from the finance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finance company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Murakami is an ordinary employee at a credit company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there is nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He gave out the loan to help his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right, the subject of an investigation should be kept secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is responsible for the debt, right? And his friend disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now the finance company wants him to pay it back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just guessed from what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's why he was being so cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was on stakeout, I noticed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it was only a split second, it was definitely those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know the name of this financial company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was going to figure that out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you guys should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Uncle, what do they want to achieve by kidnapping Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if they grab Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, they won't get their money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is the criminals' objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,One hour later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.39,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Etsuko Yano (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She use six different ATM's at two banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's definitely withdrawing a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One ATM can only withdraw not more than 2 million yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it is possible to cash out at most 5 million yen per day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, most likely she's withdrawn about 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it looks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girlfriend of the kidnapped Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Yano Etsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would Etsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scoundrels from the finance company are most likely using Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To force his girlfriend to pay off the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter from a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She definitely be able to prepare that amount of cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasn't she go to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as I can tell, she hasn't even consulted with her father yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate, she's already worn out, waiting for a call from the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to start tracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seems to be looking behind her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, the criminals told her to beware of cars that might follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the criminals noticed that Uncle was stakeout Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would believe that the detective will be accompanied by five little brats with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! It's called camouflage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was this rent car is part of a camouflage too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he just doesn't have his own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, cars are very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cost of maintaining car is also very expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the reality of being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:43.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, having her bring the money directly is very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:47.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are the criminals planning something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She turned around again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's saying something to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been following the taxi for half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver might be getting suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're slowing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they want to check whether our car will pass them or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happens if we pass them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will no longer raise suspicions, and we will also not be able to track them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they find out about us, we will not be able to track them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key of shadowing someone is to be unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even for a professional detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are exposed, then your cover will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally he caught up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you call him, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Uncle was in the bank a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went out and called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked the professor to use the spare criminal-tacking glasses to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, I can focus on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we can use the professor's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're stopping! Is this her destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they are only checking if this car is actually following them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they stopped temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we don't have a reason to stop, it will be even more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, get out of the car quickly and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! I have to go, what should I do? Oh, I'll go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, Mitsuhiko, let's get into the professor's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, stay here and keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} sit at front!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like we won this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan. We caught up with the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take the fourth Kojima intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drive past the Koichi entrance to the Okahata Highway and continue forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the shadowing method used by professional detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really need to go to the toilet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's getting a little antsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be getting closer to her destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, let's turn around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact the police for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a good time to show the skills of Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Courage and recklessness are not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you guys really want to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do something harmless and within your capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something harmless...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Within our capabilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought the money as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let go of Masaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:20:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to use you as a hostage to get money from your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you? This isn't what we promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agreements are made to be broken, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you would do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agreements are made to be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me teach you guys that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that was Izawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Yamamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaneko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with their report on the music store.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Yoshida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Tsuburai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hear to your report, "Being a Detective is Fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Detective Mouri is stakeout on someone, he becomes part of the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible for his opponent to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is how a real professionals work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, we accompanying Detective Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the first time we experienced the shadowing method used by professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:37.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Our report on the activities of Uncle and Detective Boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:41.35,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was a big success with the teacher and classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:43.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our Keron{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} hasn't been home since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost my Kamen Yaiba's card somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you find out where my friends from kindergarten are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come we don't even get any case?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like we really miscalculated...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do they only need Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please babysit my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, dad? Business is booming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Are you kidding me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe this is better suited to Uncle's talents.
